    public class BaseAcscBusImpl<TGen extends AcscGen,TLoad extends AcscLoad>
extends BaseAclfBusImpl<TGen,TLoad>
implements BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>
    An implementation of the model object 'Bus'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Sc Code
    • Seq Data Initialized
    • Pos Seq Data Initialized
    • Neg Seq Data Initialized
    • Zero Seq Data Initialized
    • Sc Gen Z1
    • Sc Gen Z2
    • Sc Gen Z0
    • Sc Load Shunt Y1
    • Sc Load Shunt Y2
    • Sc Load Shunt Y0
    • Three Seq Voltage
    • Sc Fixed Shunt Y0
    • Sc Switched Shunt Y0
    • Equiv Z1
    • Equiv Z2
    • Equiv Z0
    • Grounding
